item.title: 2020-05-07 18:00 Repair Cafe Lund @ Fixatill - Repair Cafe LUND Meetup
item.description: Do you have something to repair, want to learn more about it, or already know how to use tools and want to help others? Repair Cafe Lund is the place to go! We are a loose community of people that wants to help reducing the amount of electronic waste, loves to fix thing...
